title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Italy - Tropea Grotta Del Palombaro
description:
In this video we will fly over the Tropea Grotta Del Palombaro. The hermitage of Sant'Angelo is located in the district of Sant'Agata d'Ugno, in the valley in the municipality of Palombaro, in the province of Chieti characterized by numerous caves.
